name: DONALD J. TRUMP
description: Ugh...again with the Trump digs? I mean really, you got this far in the book...did you think I wasn't going to let up on this guy? He's the worst. I'm really trying to come off as candid and yet as intelligent as possible with you. He really is the SIN KING that is SINKING the country. At this point in 2020 literally thousands and thousands of Americans were dying daily and he did absolutely nothing. So shameful. Shame on you Trump & Co.
